				<div id="sub-head">Parents FAQ</div>	
				<div class="parent-content" >	
					<div class="head">
						<div>What is Famitivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Famtivity is a web and mobile service that simplifies the process of finding, organizing and purchasing activities. We connect activity seekers with activity providers to create a network we call The Family Activity Network.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>How do I find activities in my area?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Enter the type of activity you&#39;re seeking in the main search box. After getting results, you can enter additional criteria using the check boxes to zero in on your desired activities, date, day, gender and age.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>Can I sign up for an activity directly on Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Yes. If you have created a Famtivity account and your desired provider is also signed up to sell through Famtivity, you sign up directly on Famtivity, pay and register within the system.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>What are Discount Dollars and how do they work?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Discount Dollars are credit that you can redeem towards the purchase of any activity sold through Famtivity. You can redeem Discount Dollars for any activity that the provider has indicated qualifies for the program.  Providers determine which activities qualify and the total amount of Discount Dollars they will accept for each. You can view your dollars under the Discount Dollar tab in your profile page. When purchasing an activity you’ll be able to see your Discount Dollar total and apply them to your purchase, which is essentially a discount off the normal price.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>Can I apply Discount Dollars to activities that aren&#39;t being sold directly through Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Not at this time. However, if you invite your desired provider to join Famtivity and they sign-up for the sell-through plan, then you get a $25 credit and can then apply your Discount Dollars towards their activities.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>How do I determine the quality of an activity listed on Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>We will be adding user reviews soon.  Only those who have registered for the specific activity through Famtivity can post a review, ensuring that all reviews are both honest and relevant.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>

					<div class="head">
						<div>Does it cost more or less to sign up on Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Activities in Famtivity will usually be less than what you would pay by signing up directly with the provider. Activity providers determine registration fees for their activities, but they agree to never charge more on Famtivity. . In addition, you can apply Famtivity’s Discount Dollars towards many activities purchased through Famtivity, which gives you great deals from great providers.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>How do I get my friends to join so we can coordinate sign-ups and schedules?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Famtivity&#39;s &ldquo;Invite A Friend&rdquo; button under the &ldquo;Friends&rdquo; tab makes it easy. Simply fill out the required fields, click &lsquo;send&rsquo; and your friends will receive an invitation to join our network.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>Is there an incentive for encouraging my friends to join Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Yes. For every friend you invite, you earn $1 Discount Dollar that can be used towards purchasing any qualifying activity within the Famtivity network.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>

					<div class="head">
						<div>How do I get my favorite providers to list their activities on Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Famtivity&rsquo;s &rdquo;Invite Your Provider&ldquo; button under the &rdquo;Friends&ldquo; tab makes it easy. Simply fill out the required fields, click &lsquo;send&rsquo; and the activity provider will receive an invitation to join Famtivity.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>Is there an incentive for encouraging activity providers to join Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Yes. For each provider that you invite who joins Famtivity you receive a credit of $<%=$dollar%> Discount Dollars.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>How do I submit a review of an activity on Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>The review feature is coming soon!</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>Will my information be shared with anyone without my permission?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Absolutely not! Your privacy is extremely important to us. Famtivity will never use your information without your consent. You can change your privacy settings at any time.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
									

				</div>
				
				
