		<div id="content3">
				
				<div id="sub-head">Providers FAQ</div>	
				<div class="parent-content" >										
					<div class="head">
						<div>How will Famtivity benefit my business?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Famtivity is a one-stop shop for parents looking for activities, classes, camps and local events. Parents visit Famtivity to find and register for activities from providers just like you. We promote Famtivity on all major social networks, numerous parenting websites, and national and local websites and blogs to grow our network and create visibility for your activities - so you can get more customers.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>What are the benefits of selling activities within Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>We help parents search activities by location, age, time, day of the week, interests, availability, special needs and more. . Parents prefer to go to a one stop shop to search, register and schedule all activities. We provide you with a new set of potential customers looking for activities within our network. If you&#39;ve signed up for the &ldquo;Sell-Through&rdquo; plan, your activity can be purchased instantly by anyone who sees it, and you get a new customer that you probably wouldn&rsquo;t have otherwise.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>What do I pay to list my activities on Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Just contact us and we will automatically list your business profile and contact information at no cost.  If you want to list your specific activities, camps, classes or lessons, you can choose the <a href="javascript:void();" title="" onclick="show_pop_up(30); pop_Parent_Login('/parent_register?price=provider');show_provider_plan();  _gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Parent Module', 'clickServices','Pricing']);">monthly plan</a> that fit your specific needs.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>How do I get paid if someone purchases my activity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>We collect the fee and provide you with a direct deposit in your bank account.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>How does the Discount Dollars program work for Providers?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>When parents sign-up for Famtivity, they get &ldquo;Discount Dollars&rdquo; to use for buying activities and can also earn additional credits by inviting their friends and favorite providers to join the network.  Providers can designate which specific activities will accept Discount Dollars and how much can be applied.  For example, if you list an activity for $75 and allow for $10 in Discount Dollars to be applied as an incentive, your net revenue from the sale will be $65.  You must sign up for the Sell-Through plan to participate in the Discount Dollars program.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>

					<div class="head">
						<div>How do I create and edit my activities?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>On your profile page, click on the &ldquo;plus&rdquo; sign at the top. Simply fill out the required fields and click save to create an activity. To edit an activity, you can return to your activities page and click on the activity to edit.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>What bank information is needed to get direct deposit for activities sold within Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>We need your bank name and address, name on the account, bank routing number, and account number. This allows us to transfer money in your account when people sign up for your activities.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>

					<div class="head">
						<div>When do I receive payment for activities sold through Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>We collect and then transfer payments to your bank account each week.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>Can I use my own custom registration forms or policies inside Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Yes, go to the policies section and add your own policies as well as upload forms that attendees need to sign and submit prior to attending your activity.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>

					<div class="head">
						<div>How can I ensure that my activities are seen by the most people in Famtivity?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>One of the best ways to ensure people see your activities is by allowing for Discount Dollars to be applied to the price of your listing.  We often promote those activities that accept Discount Dollars.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
					<div class="head">
						<div>Can I change or cancel my plan once I sign up?</div>
						<div class="para"><p>Yes. Just go to the &ldquo;Plan&rdquo; area and you can upgrade, downgrade, or cancel your account at any time.</p>
						</div>					
					</div>
								
